{"tid":1552824,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"未來蘋果用戶能和 Siri 進行健康問題討論","createTime":"2019-09-08T12:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T12:53:02.000Z","uid":43178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c779a6263c99ce3aba4e4957c10cb1c4828aff","tid":1552824,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"根據《衛報》獲得的內部文件，美國 Apple 公司正在開發一種新的 Siri 語音功能，將於 2021 年秋季推出 iOS 15 版本。該功能將允許用戶就健康問題向 Siri 一次來回的對話，進行健康問題的諮詢問答，並提供機器翻譯功能。<br />\n<br />\nApple 首席執行長蒂姆庫克一再表示，Apple 公司的健康相關舉措將成為該公司&ldquo;對人類的最大貢獻&rdquo;，Siri 可能會更有能力回應身體和心理健康問題。未來 Siri 可能與 WebRX 風格的系統結合使用，將病人症狀聚合為健康建議。<br />\n<br />\nSiri 對話也可能成為 HealthKit 或 ResearchKit 的一部分，這是 Apple 在醫療領域的舉措。<br />\n<br />\nApple連醫生都做埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb4addf65ceacb2d1a0667adf726a3cd90f9c71","tid":1552824,"uid":244242,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:19:38.000Z","msg":"厲害了 我的國"},{"pid":"eb9f456b8d9429d7760eb30fe91c6fe0ebdf0e23","tid":1552824,"uid":191650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41dcecc79e74156ac630f8cd5c982dd777bf46b3","tid":1552824,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"814344a07afc05f06d921030f1df8ce0057a39cd","tid":1552824,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:53:02.000Z","msg":"開唔到醫生紙既醫生有咩用"}]}